content.protection:
A small rack is needed to get to the first bolt; draws thereafter (3 lead bolts total).  Include a set of brass or steel nuts (off-sets useful), some mid-sized stoppers, a set of cams to 1 inch, and a 2-3 inch cam (No. 3 Camalot) for the opening hand crack.  Rap from chains (shared with

Trail of Tiers

).
